    <!-- Quicker Quotes: sales reps launch "New Quicker Quote",
         so they need access to the QQ Apex the LWC/flows call. Overrules
         "avoid perm sets" non-goal to resolve the recurring (the
         dedicated perm-set has closed); object/field + Generate Order
         grants remain in draft 0059. -->
